OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells Tuesday and
OL,7,FWednesday. Cloudy start Thursday,
OL,8,Fclearing later. Breezy, especially
OL,9,Fover hills. Warm, though cooler near
OL,10,Fcoasts. Chilly by night.
